flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Receive[Warehouse Department receives physical delivery]
  Receive --> Load[System loads expected order quantities]
  Load --> Count[Unpack and count received merchandise]
  Count --> Compare{Compare received vs expected ordered}
  Compare -->|Discrepancy| Record[Record discrepancy surplus/deficit/damaged]
  Compare -->|No Discrepancy| Match[Mark as fully matched]
  
  Record --> Save[Save Goods Receipt details]
  Match --> Save
  Save --> Update[Update internal warehouse stock levels]
  Update --> End([End])
